  <brief_title>Effect of Garlic Tablet Some Indicators Related to Atherosclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Garlic Tablet on Carotid Intima Media Thickness and Flow-mediated Dilation in Patients Undergoing Angioplasty</official_title>
  <sponsors>
